# init(from:)

**Initializer**

Creates a data-value sequence from another sequence.

## Declaration

```swift
init?(from dataValue: MLDataValue)
```

## Discussion

Use this initializer to create an [doc://com.apple.createml/documentation/CreateML/MLDataValue/SequenceType] from another data-value sequence instance. You can confirm the data value’s underlying type by retrieving a non-`nil` value from [doc://com.apple.createml/documentation/CreateML/MLDataValue/sequenceValue] or by inspecting the [doc://com.apple.createml/documentation/CreateML/MLDataValue/type] property.
